prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D vector illustration of a birthday card, Unique ID 8056dccd-e65f-45a6-b3f5-bda5485ba1d8. The scene is bursting with fun, playful energy, set against a clean, light-colored background. At the center, illustrated versions of Jordan and Lao Lao from the reference photo are mid-air, joyfully leaping towards each other for a high-five. Both have huge, happy, excited expressions. Jordan wears a maroon t-shirt, and Lao Lao wears a pale yellow floral dress and glasses, consistent with the photo. Their leap is surrounded by an explosion of vibrant botanical elements: large monstera leaves, trailing ivy, whimsical ferns, and colorful abstract flower shapes in bright teal, magenta, and sunny yellow. The composition is dynamic, with leaves and petals swirling around them as if caught in their energetic motion. Below the couple, centered, the words "Happy Birthday Jordan" are written in a beautiful, elegant, and highly readable handwritten cursive script in a dark teal color. The overall style is modern, cheerful, and full of life, combining botanical beauty with playful action.
